Kyle, Leslie, Amanda, Kristina, and Caity Richmond

data.description: Turn-Key Newer Construction in Watermark! This beautiful 2-story home is just 3 years young and features modern finishes, an open-concept floor plan and plenty of space for relaxing and entertaining. The first level features maintenance free LVP throughout, a dining room/flex space and a spacious family room open to the beautiful eat-in kitchen which boasts granite counters, large island w/room for seating, walk-in pantry and SS appliances. Upstairs you'll find a versatile loft/bonus room, a beautiful primary bedroom with an ensuite bathroom and walk-in closet, along with 2 spacious secondary bedrooms and laundry room. Other notable features include smarthome technology, a two-car garage, tankless water heater, full yard irrigation, a partly brick elevation w/covered porch area and a low maintenance rear patio. Watermark will soon offer a community pool and clubhouse (under construction), access to Cosby Lake and an excellent location, just minutes away from major highways like 288, 150, 895, and 295, and it's only a 20-minute drive to Midlothian and downtown Richmond. Don't miss this opportunity!
